# Implementation Plan: Organization General Settings & AI Evaluation Config

This plan outlines the steps to connect the Organization settings page to the database and allow users to configure AI evaluation settings.

## Proposed Changes

### Database & Types

#### [MODIFY] [index.ts](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/types/index.ts)
- Update [Organization](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/types/index.ts#1-14) interface to include `goalWeight` and `aiEvaluationConfig`.

#### [SQL] Database Schema Update
- Add `goal_weight` (INTEGER DEFAULT 70) and `ai_config` (JSONB) to the `organizations` table.
- I will provide the SQL script for this.

---

### Services & Actions

#### [MODIFY] [databaseService2.ts](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/databaseService2.ts)
- Update `organizationService.getById` to fetch new columns.
- Update `organizationService.update` to save new columns.

#### [NEW] [organizationActions.ts](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/app/actions/organizationActions.ts)
- Create [getOrganizationAction()](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/app/actions/organizationActions.ts#7-29): Fetches the organization for the current authenticated user.
- Create [updateOrganizationAction(data)](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/app/actions/organizationActions.ts#30-58): Updates the organization settings.

---

### Components & Pages

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/app/(app)/organization/page.tsx)
- Change to an async server component.
- Fetch organization data using [getOrganizationAction()](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/app/actions/organizationActions.ts#7-29).
- Pass the data to [OrganizationView](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/components/organisms/OrganizationView.tsx#15-453).

#### [MODIFY] [OrganizationView.tsx](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/components/organisms/OrganizationView.tsx)
- Add `organization` prop (DONE).
- Initialize local state (org name, goal weight, submission policy) from the prop (DONE).
- **[NEW]** Initialize `selectedMetrics` from `organization.selectedMetrics`.
- **[NEW]** Connect "Save Metrics" button in the Metrics tab to [updateOrganizationAction](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/app/actions/organizationActions.ts#30-58).
- Add loading and success feedback states.

#### [MODIFY] [DashboardView.tsx](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/components/organisms/DashboardView.tsx)
- Add `organization` prop.
- Initialize `selectedMetrics` from `organization.selectedMetrics`.
- Implement a way to toggle metrics (e.g., clicking on the dashed "Add metric" card).
- When a metric is toggled, call [updateOrganizationAction](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/app/actions/organizationActions.ts#30-58) to persist the change.

#### [MODIFY] [dashboardActions.ts](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/app/actions/dashboardActions.ts)
- Update [getDashboardDataAction](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/app/actions/dashboardActions.ts#6-36) to also fetch and return the `organization` object.

