### Reporting Policies Synchronization

#### [SQL] Database Schema Update
- Add `allow_late_submissions` (BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE) to `organizations`.
- Add `require_report_submission` (BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE) to `organizations`.
- Add `notify_manager_on_submission` (BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE) to `organizations`.
- Add `global_frequency` (BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE) to `organizations`.

#### [MODIFY] [index.ts](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/types/index.ts)
- Update [Organization](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/types/index.ts#1-14) interface to include these proper fields instead of (or alongside) the JSONB `aiConfig`.

#### [MODIFY] [databaseService2.ts](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/databaseService2.ts)
- Update `organizationService` to fetch and update these new columns.

#### [MODIFY] [OrganizationView.tsx](file:///e:/Zevian%20v3/zevian-next/src/components/organisms/OrganizationView.tsx)
- Update "Reporting" tab to include the "Global Frequency" toggle.
- Ensure all toggles map to the individual database fields.
- Ensure the "Save" logic persists these fields.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- None currently available in the project.

### Manual Verification
1.  **Data Loading**:
    -   Log in and go to the **Organization** page.
    -   Verify that the organization name displayed matches the database.
2.  **Organization Rename**:
    -   Change the Organization Name to something else.
    -   Click **Save Changes**.
    -   Refresh the page and ensure the name remains updated.
3.  **AI Config Change**:
    -   Adjust the **Goal Criteria Weight** slider.
    -   Toggle **Submission Policy** settings.
    -   Click **Save Changes**.
    -   Refresh the page and ensure these settings are persisted.
4.  **Metrics Integration (Organization Page)**:
    -   Go to the **Metrics** tab in Organization settings.
    -   Select/deselect some metrics.
    -   Click **Save Metrics**.
    -   Verify that the changes are saved and reflected on the Dashboard.
5.  **Metrics Integration (Dashboard)**:
    -   On the Dashboard, find the "Organizational Metrics" section.
    -   Click "Add metric" (or similar interaction) to toggle metrics.
    -   Verify that the changes are persisted to the database and correctly update the UI.
